|YKOThe Darkwind world-wide market is a player driven economy system
that allows players to sell things on a price they set. Players
can sell things from each city's market (found near the main shop
in each city). Other players may buy from the market from most any
room on Darkwind.

Commands involved in the market are:

|YKBmarketcmds|YKO - The prompt to show all commands available for the market
             system.

|YKBmarketbuy #|YKO - This will allow a player to buy the item from the room
             in which the player is in. The money must be on hand.

|YKBmarketlist|YKO - This will display all items available for purchase on
             the market.

|YKBmarketshow #|YKO - This will display the description of the item that is
             availabe on market.

|YKBmarketmylist|YKO - This will show all the items that you have for sale
             on the market this boot.

|YKBmarketmysales|YKO - This will show you all the items that have been
             bought from you this boot.
